 </b>102.12.<b> Recognize the competence of the Committee on Migrant Workers 
</b></p>
<p><b>(Uruguay); 
 </b>102.13.<b> Ratify ICRMW, and adopt all necessary measures with the aim of 
</b></p>
<p><b>improving the treatment of migrants and asylum seekers (Argentina); 
