<p><b> </b>102.25.<b> Consider ratifying the Convention on the Prevention and Punishment 
of the Crime of Genocide (Armenia); 
</b></p>
<p><b> </b>102.26.<b> Take swift action to further enhance equality legislation, particularly 
in the area of partnership and cohabitation, as proposed by the current Maltese 
Government (Austria); 
</b></p>
<p><b> </b>102.27.<b> Consider aligning its domestic legislations and enacting new laws, as 
